[[<]]
= //<An empty hallway produces itself to the beings that occupy the space not long after, strolling down the corridor with laze. Windows appear, and flowers of many kinds grow rapidly through them. One entity, an amalgam, shifts slowly, peacefully.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] Someone has been busy, I see.

[[span class="bt"]]##fdf1f2|N/A:##[[/span]] Indeed. I must thank you; you've opened my eyes, Andry. There is far more power inside of us than we realized. I am in awe. 

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] Yes, and did you see? The cameras, O5-4--

[[span class="bt"]]##fdf1f2|N/A##[[/span]] //<Ceases walking, turning to face the other.>// Yes, yes. Andry, you did //wonderfully//. And yes, because of that, we see everything that passes through the anomaly.

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] Well, I think Four is up to something. Actually, several--

[[span class="bt"]]##fdf1f2|N/A:##[[/span]]  We see //everything//. 

= //<[[span class="bt"]]##444b47|N####ba5258|/####5c5b8e|A####744759|'#####ff8b6f|s##[[/span]] voice warps into multiple.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##ba5258|N/A:##[[/span]] //**Even you.**//

= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] steps back. The flowers on all sides wilt and turn to ash.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] What are you-- 

[[span class="bt"]]##744758|N/A:##[[/span]] We've been meaning to have a chat. Ever since you left us here, chained to this place.

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] No, I-I didn't trap you here. I was trying to protect you.

[[span class="bt"]]##ff8b6f|N/A:##[[/span]] You didn't trap us. You trapped //yourself//. We are stuck with you.

[[span class="bt"]]##ba5258|N/A:##[[/span]] And what did you actually change with your heroic acts? Who did you save? The anomaly is {{[INFOHAZARDOUS INFORMATION REMOVED]}}! Hear me? We are well past the event horizon.

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] What--? No, no, no, y-you must have gone through the gateway, this has nothing to do with me!

[[span class="bt"]]##5c5b8e|N/A:##[[/span]] This has everything to do with you. Who do you think //we// even are?

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] The Department of Delet--

[[span class="bt"]]##444b47|N/A:##[[/span]] //<Slams fist into the wall, which bends and undulates as if liquid.>// You know nothing. Deletions is //out there//. You've been played like a pawn--the //deviation// you are. And in the process, you created us. 

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] You're not making any sense. You're not thinking straight.

[[span class="bt"]]##fdf1f2|N/A:##[[/span]] //<Laughing in pentaplicate.>// Its unlikelihood is proof of its certainty. Remember? 

[[span class="bt"]]##5c5b8e|N/A:##[[/span]] We've studied you, Andry. The other We. 

[[span class="bt"]]##ff8b6f|N/A:##[[/span]] We remember you talking about the bits that slowly fall off your Semblance upon deletion. 

[[span class="bt"]]##ba5258|N/A:##[[/span]] You know, patchwork is either whole or not.

[[span class="bt"]]##444b47|N/A:##[[/span]] And maybe you haven't lost enough of yourself for us to fit in your head, but it's no matter; we just needed enough gone to reach inside and take something out. 

[[span class="bt"]]##744758|N/A:##[[/span]] Like your knowledge of how to activate the mesh, for example.

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] That's--That's not possible.

[[span class="bt"]]##5c5b8e|N/A:##[[/span]] Where are we, then? Huh?! Look around!

= //<The lighting in the hall shifts hue, settling within the ultraviolet spectrum. As a result, the chamber walls shimmer with phosphorescent lattice. The hall shifts back a moment later.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912:##[[/span]] H-How--?

= //<Before an answer could be provided, [[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] turns on a heel and sprints to the back entrance of SCP-7912's chamber. It starts as a pinpoint of light in front of him, expanding as he continues to run towards the location. When the portal increases in size to a shimmering passage, he dives through, emerging into a perfect replica of SCP-7912's once-interior. That can't be right. **Something is wrong.**>//

= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] exits the chamber into the P.M. Center's Experimentation and Neutralization wing. He takes a sharp right, the space turning into a temple, one the man had never seen before. Unfazed, he looks up at the shifting light above him. It speaks to him.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs further inside. He runs through void.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs further inside. He scales a mountain of dust and ash, coughing, each breath of opaque air labored and desperate.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs further inside. He treads a lonely desert where the sun never rises and fingers grasp at the back of his shirt.>//

[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}

= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs further inside. He hides in the awnings of furnished cabins against rainstorms that never end, from skies never seen.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]]'s steps slow aside a floating cube on an endless plane of shale. He thinks to pay it mind, but decides against. Instead, he runs further.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs up to a sterile facility and kicks the front doors open. Fortunately, they were already ajar.>//


[[span class="bt"]]##950508|THE INTERIOR:##[[/span]] {{THERE IS NO MORE OUTSIDE}}


= //<[[span class="bt"]]##783a8d|POI-7912##[[/span]] runs down a hallway, it looks familiar.>//


= //<He takes a left.>//


= //<SCP-7912's chamber awaits.>//

= {{THERE IS ONLY THE INTERIOR}}
